    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246250/extras/7721ab2fface5253040888aa87fac7dc.poster.avif?t=1739433689\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246250/extras/7721ab2fface5253040888aa87fac7dc.webm?t=1739433689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246250/extras/7721ab2fface5253040888aa87fac7dc.mp4?t=1739433689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公在生活中总是莫名其妙地被困在密室中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单却有意味深长的谜题层出不穷，解开谜底的瞬间令人倍感畅快。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■第三章</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逃脱舞台设在人间仙境的“南国度假胜地”，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公跟随亲戚来到这里度假。原计划前往酒店的巴士站，结果却被困在客房内无法离开？！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在世界一隅的南国度假胜地中，一场逃脱剧即将拉开帷幕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246250/extras/c0cc67b4d07ec179d12580d387c782fd.poster.avif?t=1739433689\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246250/extras/c0cc67b4d07ec179d12580d387c782fd.webm?t=1739433689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246250/extras/c0cc67b4d07ec179d12580d387c782fd.mp4?t=1739433689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用了全3D画面和各种巧妙机关，操作体验顺畅，包括多重结局。配备便条、相机功能等，确保从新手到逃脱专家都能简单地享受“解谜”乐趣的逃脱游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各个故事独立成章，可从随意情境开始体验。</p>",
